Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 25/12/2024
Last Updated: 25/12/2024

DJ ภูมิขี้เงี่eu ("the Bot") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the Bot on Discord.

1. Information We Collect
When you use DJ ภูมิขี้เงี่eu, we may collect the following information:

User Data:

Usernames and Discord IDs of users who interact with the Bot.
Messages or commands sent to the Bot.
Server Data:

Server IDs, channel IDs, and server settings where the Bot is added.
Roles or permissions related to the Bot’s operation.
Usage Data:

Logs of interactions with the Bot, including command usage and error reports.
2. How We Use Your Data
The data we collect is used to:

Operate and improve the functionality of the Bot.
Provide features and respond to user commands.
Troubleshoot issues and ensure the stability of the Bot.
Monitor abuse or misuse to maintain compliance with Discord’s Terms of Service.
We do not use your data for advertising or marketing purposes.

3. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell, rent, or share your data with third parties, except in the following cases:

Legal Compliance: If required by law, court order, or legal process.
Bot Development: Sharing error logs or minimal data with developers to troubleshoot or improve functionality.
Server Moderation: If explicitly requested by a server administrator for moderation purposes.
4. Data Retention
We retain your data only as long as necessary for the Bot's operation or to comply with legal obligations. Usage logs are automatically deleted after [specify time, e.g., 30 days].

If the Bot is removed from a server, associated server data will be deleted within [specify time, e.g., 7 days].

5. User Rights
As a user, you have the following rights:

Access: Request information about the data we collect about you.
Deletion: Request the deletion of your data.
Opt-out: Stop interacting with the Bot to prevent further data collection.
To exercise these rights, contact us at numthongkamm@gmail.com.

6. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

7. Children's Privacy
DJ ภูมิขี้เงี่eu is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13. If you believe we have collected such data, please contact us immediately.

8. Changes to the Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available at [insert link to Privacy Policy]. Continued use of the Bot after changes are made constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.

9. Contact Information
